name: Demam Cinta Genesis
description:
HAUS OF RIGHT NOW x KHAI (2021)

“DEMAM CINTA"" is a track written by KHAI and produced by HAUS OF RN for the upcoming project ""PANTUN X"". The track takes inspiration from the DNA remix of Suzanne Vega's ""Tom's Diner"" and tells the tale of a voyeuristic journey by a lover exploring themes of romance, lust and forbidden desires. The spoken word remix of ""DEMAM CINTA"" that utilizes of the art of sampling will be a Pink Tank exclusive accompanied by a video conceptualised by HAUS OF RN which further explores the voyeuristic nature of the song.

Please visit www.pinktank.art for more information.
